title: Arnette Witch Doctor and Drop Out A.C.E.S.
description:
Todd Richards, snowboard legend, Arnette Ambassador and all around nice guy, breaks down the Arnette Creative Exchange System (A.C.E.S.) on the new Witch Doctor and Dropout frames. Each frame in the A.C.E.S. system comes with a second set of interchangeable arms so you can change the look of your sunglasses to match your mood on any given day.

The Dropout got its inspiration from those who have better things to do with their time. A timeless medium-sized frame available in some very non-traditional colors, the Dropout matches the style of those who don't match the status quo.

A giver of sage advice, the Witch Doctor may be in his own world, but his wisdom and magic can set you on the path to greatness. Arnette's Witch Doctor frames are no different. The Witch Doctor's large lenses are housed in classic, squared-off frame that comes in a color palate that is truly otherworldly.

As a bonus, the arms on the Witch Doctor and Dropout are also compatible with the A.C.E.S. Dibs and Moolah frames, giving you even more options for customization.

Check out all the A.C.E.S. colors and styles on http://www.arnette.com
